metadata.name: WCC Zero #1
metadata.description: We are a community based project. All holders of WCC collections will physically receive their NFT. This current collection we are minting shirts, which means every holder will receive a FREE shirt courtesy of Wardrobe Collection Club. Future collections include sneakers, hats, hoodies, pants and more! We also will provide staking for holders, so you can earn passive income. Wear your Wardrobe in the Metaverse and in real-life.
